sentences: Elena Velevska (Macedonian: Елена Велевска; born October 26, 1980) is a Macedonian turbo folk and popular music singer.
In 2007, she conducted a world tour, playing in front of large diaspora audiences.
In 2008, it was announced that she is expecting a baby and therefore is having a break from the music.
She also married in beginning of the year in Ohrid.
